Given that 3 T R2* and 1.5 T R2* are in theory strictly proportional to each other, one way of converting 3 T R2* to LIC is to firstly convert 3 T R2* to 1.5 T R2* and then use a 1.5 T-R2* LIC conversion curve to calculate the LIC, Alam [6] found the relationship between 1.5 T-R2* and 3 T-R2* to be\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
